NOTE: To use the 3.0 branch of MP Forms, you'll need to checkout the formContent branch of core!

How to use the MP Test form:

1) Import the form normally.
2) Open the form for editing, make a change, undo the change, and Publish.
3) Make a note of the form ID.
4) Go to phpMyAdmin->wp_nf3_form_meta. Search for:
	parent_id 	== FORM ID
	key 		== formContentData
5) Update the value it finds with the serialised data below.
	a) If Layout & Styles is NOT active, use the first string.
	b) If Layout & Styles IS active, use the second string.
6) Preview your form.
7) If you update/publish/change your form in any way, you'll need to repeat step 5.

*
* NO LAYOUTS
*

